# Private repos referenced in README — the workflow's ambient
# GITHUB_TOKEN cannot see them (they'd 404 under any CI token scoped
# to this repo), so lychee would always fail. Existence of these repos
# is instead verified out-of-band; drift detection for public modules
# still runs via the module-status job in .github/workflows/link-check.yml.
https://github.com/LanNguyenSi/agent-control
https://github.com/LanNguyenSi/triologue
